  "parent_id": "5061188575",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1，确认AeeePro环境 2，生成cubas配置工程 3，用AeeePro打开cubas配置工程 4 模块配置"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1，确认AeeePro环境"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "cubas使用J6E_AR45__24_02 package，工具版本为 Aeee pro 2023.2.0.2， 首次使用过cubas mcu配置环境，请在工程目录 \\Platform\\stdcore\\cubas下执行_install_Toolbasetools.bat"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2，生成cubas配置工程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "在工程目录\\Cust_apl\\config\\cubas\\AEEE_mic_J6e下执行GenCubasPath.bat来生成cubas静态包文件夹快捷方式"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence2/download/attachments/228492786/image-2024-11-28_14-16-39.png?version=1&modificationDate=1732774600023&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/General Precfg for CUBAS configuration/image-2024-11-28_14-16-39.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "3，用AeeePro打开cubas配置工程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "打开toolbase AeeePro2023.2..0.2设置工作环境后，加载\\Cust_apl\\Config\\cubas\\AEEE_mic_J6e，勾选如下，进入界面后切换ABACUS,可以直接点解build确认环境是否无误，"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence2/download/attachments/228492786/image-2024-11-28_14-18-21.png?version=1&modificationDate=1732774701556&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/General Precfg for CUBAS configuration/image-2024-11-28_14-18-21.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence2/download/attachments/228492786/image-2024-11-28_14-21-37.png?version=1&modificationDate=1732774898189&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/General Precfg for CUBAS configuration/image-2024-11-28_14-21-37.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "4 模块配置"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "以上步骤没有错误即可自行配置负责的模块了，配置完成后，"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "生成在 \\Cust_apl\\Config\\cubas\\AEEE_mic_J6e\\_builds\\J6E_MASTER\\_out 路径下，请与参与编译的路径 \\Cust_apl\\Config\\cubas\\_out 比较拷贝到此路径下，才能完成配置BSW的配置；",
        "生成在 \\Cust_apl\\Config\\cubas\\AEEE_mic_J6e\\_builds\\J6E_MASTER\\_gen\\swb\\rtegen 路径下，请与参与编译的路径 \\Cust_apl\\Config\\cubas\\rtegen 比较拷贝到此路径下，才能完成配置RTE的配置；"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence2/download/attachments/228492786/image-2024-11-28_14-25-23.png?version=1&modificationDate=1732775123347&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/General Precfg for CUBAS configuration/image-2024-11-28_14-25-23.png"
    },
